    "name": "Bryson Tiller",
    "profile": "Bryson Djuan Tiller is an American singer, songwriter, and rapper. Born in Louisville, Kentucky, he started his career in 2011, releasing his debut mixtape titled “Killer Instinct Vol.1.” Tiller initially gained notable recognition following the release of his debut single, \"Don’t.” Tiller's debut studio album, “Trapsoul,” was released in October 2015 and peaked at number eight on the Billboard 200 chart. In May 2017, Tiller released his second studio album, True to Self. In 2020, Tyson released a sequel of his debut album, titled “Anniversary.” In 2021, Tiller’s first and third albums were expanded and released as vinyl exclusives.",
